text: FIFA me harna bhula toh nahin chutiye!!! Bhai woh paratha wala yaad he OAT me? kya mast banata tha be. Agli baar khelein toh draw karne ki koshish karna. All the best Bro.

text: aur bhai? Kya haal he? Kab chutiya se chaapu bangaya pata hi nahin chala. Nota se haara tha, Nota hara diya. Kya maze aye. Honestly pehle lagta tha tu HEC me kyu aagya , aakhri tak laga ki ye banda festi banjaye toh antargani achha ho jayega. Kya growth dikhayi bhai tune. Respect. All the best :)

text: TT me hara nhi paya yar, afsos reh gaya. Ghar me ghus ke haraunga ek din. Mess was better bcz of you. All the best ahead.

text:
Abe hum kya likhein? Kitna likhein? Kyu hi likhein? Likhte he to dar lagta he ki kya aage bas memoir dekh ke ek dusre ko yaad karenge? Aur jab yaad karenge to kya yaad karenge? 1st year me sutta na fukte hue bhi saath me nankari, barasirohi ya kalyanpur jaana ya miraj me last minute tkt kat ke movie dekhna ya exam ke pehle din saath me family man dekh ke exam chudwana ya phir tumhara vodka peena? Phir sochte he, yaad kyu hi karenge? bhula thodi jayega ye sab. Pehle din saath me lecture jaana chalu kiye the... abhi tak saath me PE kar rahe he. Tumhare saath jude rehne keliye humko ye memoir ki jarurat nahin he bhai.

Par yar ye memoir ek kaam toh ayega. Jab bhi aage isse dekha jayega, IT darbar jaane ka plan toh banaya hi jayega. 

Chalo be... abaad raho. Lockdown me photo bheje the, video bhejne ki koshis karte raho.
author: Pratyush Rosan Pattnaik

text: I don't want to point out incidences, but being you made me a better person. A special thanks for kavyanjali, hindi pakhwada 17.

text: Aur CEO!! Election me maje toh aye the. Aur woh PE yaad he. Saath me bhaage the fir agle class me chuda tha tu. Bhai kya maje aate he yaad karke. Fuck! bhai hein na hum? So... Suits rocks madrid suckks. all the best
author: Pratyush Rosan Pattnaik

text: Bhaiii kahe itna emotional memoir likhte ho be? muh me toh kabhi taarif nhi kia saale. You were one the closest to me in campus. You invited us to your home man. That lucknow trip was only trip I had with wingies. Jaane wala nahin tha me. Tumhi leke gayethe. There are a lot of things you know about me. I mean kaafi jyada. Thanks for keeping them secret. Honestly I was almost sure ki you will drink in our last days in college. I thought I will make that happen. But yaar sorry. Pata he, mujhe campus na jaane ka bilkul regret nahin tha. Par jab tumne us din call kiya, bht miss kiya be. Chalo bhai, humare galtiyon pe tokte rehna. Barca ke match ke time text karte rehna.
author: Pratyush Rosan Pattnaik

text: Hi argal sahab. Yaar humare pariwar ko aage badhane keliye tumse bade umeed lagaye the. Aur honestly bolte hein, tum bakchod baap bante, jo bachhon ke saath connect karta, care karta. Saath me milke cooler kharide the yaad he? We also had some really great conversastion. I miss those. Mil nahin paye yar. Sorry for that. Bahat hard working ho yar tum, great things are waiting for you. All the best.
author: Pratyush Rosan Pattnaik

text: Barca Forever man. Mereko tu bakchod lagta tha. Fir tune paytm se laptop kharida. Chutiya sala. It was fun to humiliate white crybabies together. Bakchod chaapna kuchh bhai. Fir partey karte he.
author: Pratyush Rosan Pattnaik

text: Dost Dost Dost. HEC banne tak baat tak nhi kiye the aur aakhri tak wingies ban gaye the. Campus me maje toh bahoton ke saath kiye hein, par tere saath roya hun. Saath me kaam karke bahot maja aya. Kuchh bhi impossiable nahin lagta tha. Bro, you made us roar our anthems in OAT. Aur woh bakchod catch pakda the maine tera, yaad toh hoga wo.Milte he kabhi. Fifa me haraata hu. Aur bas ek beer peete he, bas ek.
author: Pratyush Rosan Pattnaik

text: Chacha, woh soc wala project ka kya scene he? Chm ke alawa ek Hi A aya he mera. Uska shukriya. All the best man.

text:
Bhai... mereko pata he me kitna ghatiya roommate tha. Sorry for that. IITK me agar maine kuchh padha he, toh wo terese hi padha he. Bada aadmi toh banega hi tu, aur kya pata bhul bhi jayega. Par yar hum nahin bhul payenge  kabhi. 
Maje karte rehna bhai.
author: Pratyush Rosan Pattnaik

text: Bhai class he kya? Bhai assignment kiya kya? hahaha. Thank god bsbe me tu tha. Jita bio sikha he, tune sikhaya he. warna Bando ke course me abtak fakka hota. My whole academic career owes you a lot. Baki yaar wing ka sabse perfect banda he tu. Sab kuchh karleta he. I can't write things about you. I can't. Pata nhi kya kya yaad aa rha. kya kya likhun. I am very connected with my childhood friends. Before we were friends, I thought I won't have a friend like that again.  Because you were the first person I felt connected to in campus. I always felt left out during our orientation. I actually didn't meet anyone like me. Lekin jab baap meeting me baapu log bolte he blue packet kholne ko, do log bolte he humne packet kho diya. Tu or me. I was sure we were going to be great friends.  Aur tu school me acting sikha he, ye pata he humko. Pachas baar batane ki jarurat nhi he. Saath me galaxy haare hein, saath me galaxy jeete hein, High bhi hue hein low bhi. Par badminton me achha khel leta hu. Milenge toh bht bhand honge. De dena jitna gaali dena ho. Shots marenge har gaali pe. Chal bhai. Chaapte rehna.
author: Pratyush Rosan Pattnaik
